div.div: Boku no Kokoro no Yabai Yatsu

Fascinated by murder and all things macabre, Kyoutarou daydreams of acting out his twisted fantasies on his unsuspecting classmates but an encounter with Anna Yamada, the gorgeous class idol, lights a spark in the darkness of his heart. Its a classic tale of an antisocial boy falling for a popular girl, but neither are who they appear to be at first glance. Will Kyoutarou and Anna defy their expectations of each other and of themselves?
(Source: HIDIVE)
